<th>用途</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><code v-pre>Consumer&lt;T&gt;</code>消费型接口</td>
<td><code v-pre>T</code></td>
<td><code v-pre>void</code></td>
<td>接收一个参数，没有返回值</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code v-pre>BiConsumer</code>消费型接口</td>
<td><code v-pre>T,U</code></td>
<td><code v-pre>void</code></td>
<td>接收两个参数，没有返回值</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code v-pre>Supplier&lt;T&gt;</code>供给型接口</td>
<td>无</td>
